## ‚ôø Accessibility (WCAG 2.2 AA)
- **Landmarks:** Use `<header>`, `<nav>`, `<main>`, `<footer>`, `<section>`.
- **Keyboard operability:** All interactive elements must be keyboard accessible. Focus traps in modals. Escape closes dialogs.
- **Visible focus:** Always provide visible focus styles.
- **Forms:** Inputs must have labels, helper text, and inline error messages with `aria-live`.
- **Colour & motion:** Maintain text contrast ‚â• 4.5:1. Respect reduced motion preferences.
- **Images:** Always provide meaningful `alt`. Decorative images use empty `alt`.

